# Epic 1: Receipt Capture & Processing

## Description
Core receipt capture with OCR, batch processing, edge detection, and retry mechanisms

## Stories
- 1.1: Batch Receipt Capture
- 1.2: Auto Edge Detection
- 1.3: OCR Confidence Scores
- 1.4: Retry Failed Captures
- 1.5: Image Enhancement
- 1.6: Multi-Page Support
- 1.7: Camera Settings
